'''''Winnie the Pooh''''' is an American [[The Walt Disney Company|Walt Disney Company]] [[Media franchise|franchise]], based on animated [[fictional characters]] who have been featured as part of the [[List of Disney characters|Disney character line-up]]. The ''Winnie the Pooh'' franchise is based on the book by [[A. A. Milne]]. '''''Winnie-the-Pooh''''' (with hyphenation), is the first volume of stories about [[Winnie-the-Pooh|a bear of the same name]], by A. A. Milne, from 1926, upon which the franchise is based.
